{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-article-tsx","path":"/academy/blog/posts/an-easy-guide-on-how-to-buy-crypto-on-deriv/","result":{"data":{"directus":{"blog":[{"id":"a2088b80-4d5b-4e76-8544-c99c1d78e312","blog_title":"An easy guide on how to buy crypto on Deriv","meta_title":"An easy guide on how to buy crypto on Deriv","meta_description":"Eager to jump on the crypto bandwagon? Here is how you can buy crypto with Deriv’s fiat onramp services and start trading.","og_title":"How to buy crypto on Deriv","og_description":"Eager to jump on the crypto bandwagon? Here is how you can buy crypto with Deriv’s fiat onramp services and start trading.","test_data":false,"published_date":"2022-02-17","blog_post":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Buying crypto to fund your Deriv cryptocurrency account just got easier with our new fiat onramp services. In this article, we&rsquo;ll go through what a fiat onramp is and how it works.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Significant and rapid price fluctuations of cryptocurrencies present many opportunities to profit from them, and if you plan to take part in the crypto action, keeping up with the latest trends is essential. One way to jump onto the crypto bandwagon with Deriv is to </span><a href=\"https://deriv.com/academy/blog/posts/trading-with-crypto-top-3-myths\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">trade </span><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">with</span></em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> crypto</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, as it gives a great opportunity to gain more crypto while trading on your favourite markets.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Before you can start trading with crypto on one of our platforms, you&rsquo;ll first need to own some. And if you see an upcoming opportunity to profit on one of the markets, you certainly don&rsquo;t want any delays in funding your account and opening your first trades. The easiest and fastest way to fund your Deriv crypto account is to exchange your fiat currency for cryptocurrency. This process has become much easier than before with fiat to crypto exchange services, also called fiat onramps.</span></p>\n<h2><strong>What is a fiat to crypto exchange?</strong></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fiat onramps are services that create a bridge between fiat currency and crypto on the trading platform of your choice. They allow you to purchase cryptocurrency in exchange for your fiat deposit, helping you get your Deriv crypto account ready for trading on our platforms quickly and efficiently.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Onramp services are available globally, no matter where you are in the world, and they handle the entire exchange process. It can be a perfect solution if you want to start trading with crypto but don&rsquo;t own any. On Deriv, you can trade with Bitcoin (BTC), Litecoin (LTC), Ethereum (ETH), Tether (USDT) Omni, Tether (USDT) ERC-20, and USD coin (USDC). Once you create a Deriv cryptocurrency account, the digital coins you buy through our fiat onramp solutions will be deposited directly into it. There is no need to create a separate cryptocurrency wallet.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<h2><strong>Which fiat onramp services does Deriv currently offer?</strong></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">At the moment, Deriv offers three onramp solutions that allow our clients to exchange fiat for crypto quickly and easily to start trading on our platforms.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">These onramps are Changelly, Banxa, and Xanpool. Each one of them is automatically set to offer you the digital coin matching your Deriv cryptocurrency account.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Let&rsquo;s choose </span><a href=\"https://changelly.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Changelly</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> as an example to explain how it all works.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Changelly can provide you with a totally seamless trading experience. It&rsquo;s a crypto exchange that&rsquo;s speedy, safe, and available all over the world.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Deposits via Changelly can take between 5-30 minutes to be processed, depending on the cryptocurrency chosen and current transaction capacity of a blockchain. Deposits are available in USD, and you can add between 50 USD to 5,000 USD in a single go.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You simply need to choose your location, get verified, and you&rsquo;ll receive coins directly to your Deriv cryptocurrency account within 30 minutes.</span></p>\n<p>Here is what you need to do to buy crypto via Changelly:</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">1. Log in to </span><a href=\"https://deriv.com/signup/?utm_source=deriv-blog&amp;utm_medium=blog&amp;utm_campaign=ww-pr-deriv-all-0221-en&amp;utm_content=onramp-solution-changelly\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">app.deriv.com</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> real account and switch to your cryptocurrency account.</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://deriv-academy.directus.app/assets/67386e6e-7229-4d1d-9773-3a2c8ccfb4c9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><img src=\"https://deriv-academy.directus.app/assets/67386e6e-7229-4d1d-9773-3a2c8ccfb4c9\" alt=\"Log in to Your Deriv Cryptocurrency Account\" width=\"1650\" height=\"1116\" /></span></em></a></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">2. Click Cashier.</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://deriv-academy.directus.app/assets/cf60e529-451b-4e8c-8a2e-e6bd293cf7bf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://deriv-academy.directus.app/assets/cf60e529-451b-4e8c-8a2e-e6bd293cf7bf\" alt=\"Select Cashier in Your Deriv Cryptocurrency Account\" width=\"1651\" height=\"1116\" /></a></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3. Select Fiat onramp.</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://deriv-academy.directus.app/assets/48818170-08eb-4dd7-9baf-9fd7570f8153\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://deriv-academy.directus.app/assets/48818170-08eb-4dd7-9baf-9fd7570f8153\" alt=\"Select Fiat Onramp in Your Cryptocurrency Account\" width=\"1651\" height=\"1116\" /></a></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">4. Choose Changelly.</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://deriv-academy.directus.app/assets/81f0cc73-e38e-4698-a27c-0831b1a27845\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://deriv-academy.directus.app/assets/81f0cc73-e38e-4698-a27c-0831b1a27845\" alt=\"Choose Fiat Onramp in Your Deriv Cryptocurrency Account\" width=\"1651\" height=\"1115\" /></a></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">5. You&rsquo;ll be redirected to the Changelly website, where you&rsquo;ll need to select a payment method, your location and an amount of crypto to buy.</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://deriv-academy.directus.app/assets/b8c32b9f-4209-4c4d-acaa-42809e43726b\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://deriv-academy.directus.app/assets/b8c32b9f-4209-4c4d-acaa-42809e43726b\" alt=\"Buy Crypto with Deriv&rsquo;s Fiat Onramp Services\" width=\"1651\" height=\"1116\" /></a></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">6. Create an account with your basic details, add a payment method and proceed with the transaction. Once done, you&rsquo;ll be sent back to Deriv.</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://deriv-academy.directus.app/assets/63a1a0f6-450c-41f0-9d0d-7634387cd752\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://deriv-academy.directus.app/assets/63a1a0f6-450c-41f0-9d0d-7634387cd752\" alt=\"Buy Crypto with Deriv&rsquo;s Fiat Onramp Services 2\" width=\"1651\" height=\"1115\" /></a></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Now, you&rsquo;re ready to start trading with crypto on Deriv. </span><a href=\"https://deriv.com/signup/?utm_source=deriv-blog&amp;utm_medium=blog&amp;utm_campaign=ww-pr-deriv-all-0221-en&amp;utm_content=onramp-solution-changelly\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sign up for a </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Deriv </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">account </span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">now to start using our fiat onramp services and begin your trading adventure.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Disclaimer:</span></em></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><em data-stringify-type=\"italic\">Cryptocurrency accounts and Fiat Onramp payment methods are not available for clients residing within the EU. </em><em data-stringify-type=\"italic\">This content is not intended for clients residing in the UK.</em></span></p>","author":{"id":"0d7772f6-5338-488f-a8aa-adfb6c5074b9","name":"The Deriv team","image":{"id":"9826d676-357b-4683-8f80-28a4ef931f91","description":"Deriv Logo","imageFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8f8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/2efee03fa50ea098c4f945ea8267e57d/de3a1/deriv%20profile%20pic.png","srcSet":"/static/2efee03fa50ea098c4f945ea8267e57d/f2a56/deriv%20profile%20pic.png 38w,\n/static/2efee03fa50ea098c4f945ea8267e57d/7458e/deriv%20profile%20pic.png 75w,\n/static/2efee03fa50ea098c4f945ea8267e57d/de3a1/deriv%20profile%20pic.png 150w","sizes":"(min-width: 150px) 150px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/2efee03fa50ea098c4f945ea8267e57d/0852d/deriv%20profile%20pic.webp 38w,\n/static/2efee03fa50ea098c4f945ea8267e57d/18188/deriv%20profile%20pic.webp 75w,\n/static/2efee03fa50ea098c4f945ea8267e57d/c65bc/deriv%20profile%20pic.webp 150w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 150px) 150px, 100vw"}]},"width":150,"height":150}}}}},"main_image":{"id":"fd05cb56-40de-465d-80af-ea1d06ece3b0","description":"An Easy Guide on How to Buy Crypto on Deriv","imageFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","background